r size) radius\nof the ice ball and small (nanometer size) thickness of the water shell\nsurrounding the ice. These results might be relevant to the formation of hail\nin thunderclouds. These results are tentative in that the self-energies are\nomitted; surface tension and nucleation energy are not considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Jul 2019 17:40:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Jan 2020 13:09:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
