ssuming the Exponential Time\nHypothesis: $f_H(tw)=2^{\\Theta(tw)}$ if $H$ is a contraction of the chair or\nthe banner, and $f_H(tw)=2^{\\Theta(tw\\cdot \\log tw)}$ otherwise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Jul 2019 22:29:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Mar 2021 15:18:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-12"}
