elation is good for values of the\nCE energy efficiency parameter, $\\alpha{_{\\rm{CE}}}$, in the range 0.1--0.3.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jul 2019 05:31:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-11"}
