ntify\nsingle and multiple atom counts. This probabilistic approach will find\napplications in cavity QED studies in dense atomic media and paves the way\ntowards realizing coherent quantum control schemes in large-scale macroscopic\nsystems aimed at out of the lab quantum devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jul 2019 12:52:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
