e algae and cyanobacteria\ncould extend it to over 2 Gyr ago, expanding the use of a photosynthetic red\nedge to earlier times in Earth's history.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jul 2019 12:02:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-12"}
